ed="T" n="0817a18"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0817a18"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>洛陽同德寺<persName key="A004220">無名</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0817a19"/><persName key="A004220">釋無名</persName>，姓高氏，<placeName key="PL000000022574">渤海</placeName>人也。祖宦今<placeName key="PL000000023603">西京</placeName>，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0817a20"/>為<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>人矣。沖孺之齡，舉措卓異，口不嚌<lb
ed="T" n="0817a21"/>辛血，性不狎諠譁，邈矣出塵，故難留滯。<lb
ed="T" n="0817a22"/><date key="j19949921995356" from-iso="+0750-01-01" to-iso="+0750-12-31">年二十八</date>，若瘦雁之出籠，投師習學，依隨<lb
ed="T" n="0817a23"/>隷<placeName key="PL000000023593">同德寺</placeName>。及精《律藏》，解一字以無疑；聞<lb
ed="T" n="0817a24"/>有禪宗，思千里而請決。舉領整裘，開扃見<lb
ed="T" n="0817a25"/>路，辭飛筆健，思若湧泉。因隨師遊方，訪祖<lb
ed="T" n="0817a26"/>師之遺跡，得<persName key="A005612">會師</persName>付授心印。<persName key="A005612">會</persName>先語諸徒<lb
ed="T" n="0817a27"/>曰：「<persName key="A005612">吾</persName>之付法，無有名字。」因號<persName key="A004220">無名</persName>也。自此<lb
ed="T" n="0817a28"/>志歷四方，周遊<placeName key="PLG00000000002">五嶽</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000031276">羅浮</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬阜</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000016742">雙峯</placeName>、<anchor xml:id="beg0817sgsz1"/>𡷗<anchor xml:id="end0817sgsz1"/>公<!--找不到此地-->、<anchor xml:id="beg0817sgsz3"/>鑢<anchor xml:id="end0817sgsz3"/><lb
ed="T" n="0817a29"/>嶺<!--找不到此地-->、<placeName key="PL000000008579">牛頭</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013448">剡溪</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013191">若耶</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000012277">四明</placeName>，罔不<anchor xml:id="beg0817002"/>詢<anchor xml:id="end0817002"/>問，風<pb ed="T" n="0817b" xml:id="T50.2061.0817b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0817b01"/>格高遠，神操朗澈，博識者覩貌便伏，僻見者<lb
ed="T" n="0817b02"/>發言必摧。時<persName key="A001671">德宗</persName>方納<persName key="A011933">鮮于叔明</persName>、<persName key="A011935">令狐峘</persName>料<lb
ed="T" n="0817b03"/>簡僧尼事，時<persName key="A004220">名</persName>有表直諫，並停。尋時<persName key="A011933">鮮于<lb
ed="T" n="0817b04"/>叔明</persName>、<persName key="A011935">令狐峘</persName>等流<placeName key="PL000000030463">南海</placeName>百姓。至<date from-iso="+0790-01-24" key="j20096252010008" to-iso="+0791-02-11"><name>貞元</name>六年</date>，往<lb
ed="T" n="0817b05"/>遊<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>，居無定所。<date key="j20110842011084" when-iso="+0794-01-22">九年十二月十二日</date>於<lb
ed="T" n="0817b06"/><placeName key="PL000000005371">佛光寺</placeName>先食訖，儼然坐化，春秋七十二，臘四<lb
ed="T" n="0817b07"/>十三。十一年闍維，獲舍利一升。澤潞<!--找不到此地-->節度使<lb
ed="T" n="0817b08"/><persName key="A010454">李抱真</persName>建塔於<placeName key="PL000000005371">佛光寺</placeName>，<date from-iso="+0790-01-24" key="j20096252010008" to-iso="+0791-02-11"><name>貞元</name>六年庚午歲</date>也。<lb
ed="T" n="0817b09"/>或云：「<persName key="A004220">名</persName>著《疏》解《彌陀經》焉。」</p>
